        <mxCell id="yhUPL6oVbNzLrTyTOgMJ-26" value="Flattened Image Tree - FIT is the single binary that can contain multiple images with metadata for storing image information along with singnature&lt;div&gt;Secure boot is using to generate a FIT image contains kernel , device tree, initframfs. FIT images is singed using private key. also the signature is store in FIT.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Public Key is store in the bootloader . signed bootloader be authenticate by ROM Code&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
